nf-core is a global, open-source community that develops curated, best-practice
bioinformatics analysis pipelines using the workflow manager Nextflow. It
standardizes how complex genetic and biological data is processed by ensuring
pipelines are highly reproducible, portable across different computing
environments, and automated through software containerization
"

